,{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is a UI element that allows to present recommended or predictive options based on user’s input or context,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and is commonly used to capture filtering decisions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Suggestion chip is typically non-selected by default and can be tapped or clicked to apply the suggestion, streamlining input and enhancing usability."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Chips can show multiple interactive elements together in the same area, such as a list of selectable movie times, or a serie of email contacts."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Best suited for category-based filters that do not require additional visual elements."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSuggestionChip"}],"title":"OUDSSuggestionChip","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSuggestionChip/accessibilityActivationPoint(_:isEnabled:)-51dg8":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSuggestionChip\/accessibilityActivationPoint(_:isEnabled:)-51dg8","title":"accessibilityActivationPoint(_:isEnabled:)","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"accessibilityActivationPoint","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI9UnitPointV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnitPoint"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"isEnabled","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ModifiedContent","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI15ModifiedContentV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"